{"tid":1341320,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"你地班垃圾連登仔 我笑鳩你地啊","createTime":"2019-07-21T16:37:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-21T17:02:23.000Z","uid":13169,"like":11,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"5471ab20e100d56e4c83aaf2814d44ca9a761de5","tid":1341320,"uid":13169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T16:37:12.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">sorry呃你哋入嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n屌你老母元朗單嘢睇到我堅嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n玩左幾年音樂<br />\n同大家介紹件好使好用嘅樂器<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rLCkdqJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrLCkdqJ.png&h=b7943abb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一棍在手 出街可以玩音樂又唔怕有人對你做啲咩<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">擋又得玩人體敲擊音樂</span></span><br />\n平個啲$30-40就有一對<br />\n有咩事斷左 換個對又得 反正咁平大家買多幾對去同人玩下敲擊樂都唔怕啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家唔好買啲垃圾棍啊！！！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家識做啦"},{"pid":"46c37549d691fe39d0939c9494fcfa96c5690f07","tid":1341320,"uid":177089,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T16:37:56.000Z","msg":"太短<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mqw5pHh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fmqw5pHh.png&h=ed84f619&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"619c1f15365bc0ee877064f1899ba0df0100cf61","tid":1341320,"uid":13169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T16:40:18.000Z","msg":"我無野請"},{"pid":"17ed51bddead1d11106a7d6cede74b7